annotationA: Augmin complex subunit msd5; As part of the augmin complex, plays a role in centrosome-independent generation of spindle microtubules. The complex is required for mitotic spindle assembly through its involvement in localizing gamma-tubulin to spindle microtubules
annotationB: Augmin complex subunit dgt5; As part of the augmin complex, plays a role in centrosome-independent generation of spindle microtubules. The complex is required for mitotic spindle assembly through its involvement in localizing gamma-tubulin to spindle microtubules
